    All Classes and Interfaces

    Classes
    Class
    Description
    Cell
    A class which represents a single cell in the data table.
    DataTable
    The table which stores all the textual data for a graph.
    FileDataManager
    A utility class which interfaces between an open file and a project.
    Graph
    The visual graph associated with a project.
    GraphPanel
    A class intended to be composited under a Graph, showing only the graphical portion of the graph window.
    GraphPoint
    A class holding one X/Y point and associated error bars.
    Main
    The main class of the grapher, in charge of managing other windows and storing constants.
    MenuBar
    A menu bar that is attached to all windows and holds commands that allow for easier manipulation of the project.
    PlottableData
    A class which stores a single set of plottable data.
    PlottableDataMenu
    A menu used as part of the PlottableTable to configure a single PlottableData set.
    PlottableTable
    A graphical data table which stores all the data to be entered into a graph.
    RotatedLabel
    A class storing a JLabel rotated by an arbitrary amount.
    Series
    A class which loosely "holds" any number of Cells in a doubly linked list.
    SeriesHeader
    A class that allows for editing the name of a series.
    SeriesSelector
    A custom dropdown menu that allows for the selection of a single series from the DataTable.
